<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>SF Hacks Check-in QR Code</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
    
    <div style="max-width: 600px; background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: auto; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h2 style="color: #007bff;">SF Hacks Check-in QR Code</h2>
